{"tid":436044,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地一日食幾餐？","createTime":"2017-10-14T19:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T08:23:36.000Z","uid":69522,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8950e58da05d450c449dc79fcc70015ed970019a","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:33:50.000Z","msg":"每次食完野好快就肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論食幾多野，幾飽都好（包括自助餐 放題）<br />\n感覺隔2-3個鐘就消化哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就開始有肚餓既感覺<br />\n4-5個鐘就好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一定要搵野食<br />\n<br />\n之前中學雞年代，試過食自助餐，頭半粒鐘食到好飽，但係臨走個陣又覺得消化完想食野，但係其他人話要走，最後餓住咁離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一日三餐對我黎講完全唔夠，至少四餐先可以滿足，如果夜晚遲瞓要五餐先夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n8點食完晚飯，11點到就想食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過冇食到，拖到宜家3點好肚餓，啱啱食完3條蕉，但係個肚完全無感覺有食到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想知有冇巴絲都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：一日多過三餐<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：一日三餐"},{"pid":"f9be7ddae3662ea9ba73ab2fc55c06d8a910d96b","tid":436044,"uid":144224,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:37:12.000Z","msg":"一日少過三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3fef7ea10438ac7348e90becfdbdf831ee3c63","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:37:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一日少過三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點樣做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4c7250a853ef9c16cdfebdbdc9b62981c5d714","tid":436044,"uid":91989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:38:36.000Z","msg":"五餐先係mini-requirement for survival"},{"pid":"a8a72f47b96e988a4e66f8ccfda82993f5b985eb","tid":436044,"uid":59612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:38:57.000Z","msg":"巴打肥唔肥先？"},{"pid":"b812f6688f0212a4eb56b3ff5397358489fa4b18","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>五餐先係mini-requirement for survival</blockquote><br />\n巴打好大食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de7a8cb8bbe0b3f2891d5765cedf7b4c931b47a","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:40:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打肥唔肥先？</blockquote><br />\n50kg 17x 非洲難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ae34b3d2a47826aec281102b6d0705a8eb959b","tid":436044,"uid":88944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:40:34.000Z","msg":"一日最多兩餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想一日四餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"908bd395386df16e33b419a453434863814fa57f","tid":436044,"uid":59612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:40:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打肥唔肥先？</blockquote><br />\n50kg 17x 非洲難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我情況差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0137b24413cf9c5661699d4ae65ce6741c974af","tid":436044,"uid":59612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:42:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打肥唔肥先？</blockquote><br />\n50kg 17x 非洲難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我情況差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日都比屋企人話係咪生蟲"},{"pid":"6715e98f068a1a3e6d27b082da642099b09169c7","tid":436044,"uid":144224,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一日少過三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點樣做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日都係因為太趕或者瞓過頭食唔到早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0624ed776d26560e56b2c2545644883728a56a","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:42:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打肥唔肥先？</blockquote><br />\n50kg 17x 非洲難民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我情況差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n食極都唔肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fca05efb49f5a6bbd9df34b8bdea124cb705ff7","tid":436044,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:43:56.000Z","msg":"早餐 午餐 下午茶 晚餐 宵夜<br />\n其實點為之一餐?我食幾個水果/生果都叫一餐?"},{"pid":"205428f9da4f0f0d57175b669fce29eab666d530","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:45:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一日少過三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點樣做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日都係因為太趕或者瞓過頭食唔到早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我唔食早餐會完全無精神，直到食lunch為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15139a8c0834c1539bc4e0bc37da8947a66d3329","tid":436044,"uid":15792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:46:36.000Z","msg":"基本上食完一餐會即刻肚餓"},{"pid":"6fa68183a6c4354dddfb00970fa60f151699556e","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:47:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早餐 午餐 下午茶 晚餐 宵夜<br />\n其實點為之一餐?我食幾個水果/生果都叫一餐?</blockquote><br />\n我係餐廳點一個餐為之一餐，最少m記一個餐份量"},{"pid":"eff0c3857280534a58f6549d7abbec0ca8c49553","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:47:48.000Z","msg":"宜家仲餓緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d73239749ada981ddde91aa8627f971ef07f5a","tid":436044,"uid":37414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:47:54.000Z","msg":"其實食多d餐數先對個消化系統好"},{"pid":"6584b9ab429dad51fa5ee8ad711f5bcb9dc9f895","tid":436044,"uid":91989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:48:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>五餐先係mini-requirement for survival</blockquote><br />\n巴打好大食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我阿媽問我肚係生蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但真係好快肚餓"},{"pid":"a21f28ea51c1912709653cec0c9ae557cbaa700d","tid":436044,"uid":144224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一日少過三餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你點樣做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n日日都係因為太趕或者瞓過頭食唔到早餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果我唔食早餐會完全無精神，直到食lunch為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前我都係同你一樣，但而家冇感覺了，食到當好彩，食唔到都冇所謂"},{"pid":"5bfbc901f660fe28b4501936c177e3e2d19d720f","tid":436044,"uid":58140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T19:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早餐 午餐 下午茶 晚餐 宵夜<br />\n其實點為之一餐?我食幾個水果/生果都叫一餐?</blockquote><br />\n我係餐廳點一個餐為之一餐，最少m記一個餐份量</blockquote><br />\n諗起以前一日都係三餐 但餐餐份量都好大<br />\n自從大病之後 宜家食量少左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想試下食到好飽嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dce812991eb3becc45f6814cbbc9bbb53849a2be","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-14T20:02:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實食多d餐數先對個消化系統好</blockquote><br />\n但係返工返學未必就到時間食咁多餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efd82013a95b225cdf893e7204abe3ac94442480","tid":436044,"uid":18800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:07:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02aa3a1edfbbd3c2f30619210b823612f8a0e011","tid":436044,"uid":69522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T08:23:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早餐 午餐 下午茶 晚餐 宵夜<br />\n其實點為之一餐?我食幾個水果/生果都叫一餐?</blockquote><br />\n我係餐廳點一個餐為之一餐，最少m記一個餐份量</blockquote><br />\n諗起以前一日都係三餐 但餐餐份量都好大<br />\n自從大病之後 宜家食量少左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想試下食到好飽嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有次大病之後就食極都唔肥  一直都係排骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 健康檢查話要做多d運動先容易吸收<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}